Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.60,0:04:31.78,TEXT JP UP,,0,0,0,,Your hope is gone now
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.78,0:04:34.13,TEXT JP UP,,0,0,0,,No one cares, No one's here
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.13,0:04:40.06,TEXT JP UP,,0,0,0,,Shut your eyes and sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.06,0:04:42.52,TEXT JP UP,,0,0,0,,Just sleep now
